# Skill: Auto-Fix GitHub Issues

Resout automatiquement les issues GitHub labellees "{{ autofix_label | default('auto-fix') }}" via Claude Code sur le RPi.

## Quand utiliser ce skill

- Issue GitHub avec label `auto-fix` recue via n8n
- Erreur de prod detectee par monitoring necessitant un fix code
- Demande de correction de bug simple (lint, typo, config)

## Pipeline

Le pipeline est orchestre par n8n (workflow `github-autofix`).
Ce skill documente le processus pour les agents qui participent.

## Repos supportes

{% for repo in autofix_repos | default([]) %}
- `{{ repo.name }}` ({{ repo.url }}) — agent par defaut : {{ repo.default_agent }}
{% endfor %}

## Flux

```
GitHub Issue (label "{{ autofix_label | default('auto-fix') }}")
  → Webhook n8n (/webhook/github-autofix)
    → Validation HMAC (X-Hub-Signature-256)
    → Parse issue + route agent
    → Plane work item "in-progress" (via Messenger)
    → SSH vers RPi → claude-autofix <repo_url> <issue_id> <title> <body>
      → git clone/pull
      → branch fix/GH-{id}
      → Claude Code --dangerously-skip-permissions
      → git push + gh pr create
    → Plane work item "done" + pr_url (via Messenger)
    → Telegram notification
```

## Resultat attendu

- Branche : `fix/GH-{issue_id}`
- PR creee avec reference `Fixes #{issue_id}`
- Commit co-author: `Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>`
- CI doit passer (lint + tests)
- Review humaine obligatoire avant merge

## Plane tracking

Le suivi Plane passe toujours par le Messenger via `sessions_spawn` :

```
# Creation du work item au debut du fix :
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: create_task projectId=<id> name=🔧 Auto-fix GH-{id}: {title} description_html=<p>Issue: {url}</p> priority=high")
-> Retourne: work_item_id

# Passage en cours :
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: update_task workItemId=<work_item_id> state=<uuid_in_progress>")

# Labels :
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: create_label projectId=<id> name=auto-fix color=#ef4444")
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: create_label projectId=<id> name=github color=#1d4ed8")

# A la fin (PR creee) :
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: add_comment workItemId=<work_item_id> comment_html=<p>[DELIVERABLE] PR #{pr_number} — {pr_url}</p>")
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: update_task workItemId=<work_item_id> state=<uuid_done>")
```

## Limitations

- Ne PAS traiter les issues de securite critique (tag `security`)
- Ne PAS modifier les secrets ou fichiers vault
- Max 1 issue traitee simultanement par repo
- Timeout SSH : 10 minutes (issues complexes)
